entries.text: Hi, I'm calling from outside the US regarding an international order. My name is Maria Garcia.
Hello Maria. To assist you, could you please provide your passport number for verification?
Yes, my passport number is G12345678. I also have a question about customs fees.
Thank you for that. I'm verifying your details now. What is your question about customs fees?
I was charged an unexpected fee. Can you tell me why? My order number is INT987654.
I see. For international orders, customs duties and taxes are typically applied by your local authorities upon arrival. This is standard procedure.
Ah, I understand now. Thank you for clarifying. I appreciate your help!
